        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p>[<em><a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/mass-prisoners-could-choose-between-freedom-and-their-organs/?utm_source=newsletter-email&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=newsletter-article\">View in browser</a></em>]</p>"
