          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Massachusetts Democrats have a bold new proposal for prisoners: donate your organs or bone marrow, and get as little as a couple of months off of your sentence. The legislation, which has attracted five cosponsors in the state House, raises major bioethical concerns for the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
