            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "A five-member ‚ÄúBone Marrow and Organ Donation Committee,‚Äù only one of whom is designated to be a prisoners‚Äô rights advocate, would decide how much time off prisoners would receive from donating organs.",
